      <title>X 告訴巴西法院，「操作故障」讓被封鎖的使用者保持活躍狀態</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/x-tells-brazil-court-operational-faults-allowed-blocked-users-remain-active-2024-04-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西 X 的代表律師週五向最高法院表示，「操作失誤」使得被封鎖的用戶仍能在社群媒體平台上保持活躍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/x-tells-brazil-court-operational-faults-allowed-blocked-users-remain-active-2024-04-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 20:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
